708131f-a.title: Manhattan: 3rd Avenue - 88th Street
708131f-a.text:
Third Ave., west side, north of East 88th Street and showing at 89th
Street, a station of the Third Ave. Elevated Line.
November 14, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

708132f-a.title: Manhattan: 3rd Avenue - 88th Street
708132f-a.text:
Third Avenue, east side, from 88th to 89th Streets, showig 1569
Third Avenue, on the N. E. corner of 88th Street, a three-
story frame house with a stone front.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection,Museum of the City of New York,
Negative No. 235,
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.
